reviewText:
Excellent! Can't find any better. Remember don't be like the dummies in the other reviews and expect the sound to be perfect because these were recorded in the 50's.
They sound just fine for cruising around town or playing in the kitchen.

I really like this as I have a long commute to town and work. I gave
it only 4 stars because it has several shows that are repeated on the
same cd. and also some of them are really hard to hear but mostly
they are great.
Gunsmoke Old Time Radio Mp3 5 CD's, the CD's were exactly what I wanted for my long commute to work, I am happy with the purchase, Thank you very much.
Fast service and good quality. Have had no problems with recordings like I have had with others. Am very happy with them. Will use again if needed.
